active in his church.

180
00:07:37,762 --> 00:07:38,932
他的邻居和同事
The neighbors and coworkers

181
00:07:38,932 --> 00:07:40,482
对此都感到非常震惊
that we've spoken to expressed shock.

182
00:07:40,482 --> 00:07:42,172
谁都没想到会发生这样的事
None of them saw this coming.

183
00:07:42,172 --> 00:07:44,522
他的动机目前还不明确
His motive is not yet known,

184
00:07:44,522 --> 00:07:46,802
