of Gavin Bryant's suicide note.

903
00:39:00,828 --> 00:39:02,838
盖文自杀后还留言了吗
Gavin left a suicide note?

904
00:39:02,838 --> 00:39:04,568
有意思 上面写什么了
Well, that's beautiful. What'd it say?

905
00:39:04,568 --> 00:39:06,068
你查的这些悬案里面
In your cold case files here,

906
00:39:06,068 --> 00:39:08,408
有查到一个叫安娜的人吗
you find anything involving someone named Anna?

907
00:39:08,408 --> 00:39:10,038
安娜 
Anna. Uh...

908
00:39:10,038 --> 00:39:12,708
好像有个强奸案和凶杀案里有
Maybe one in rape and one in homicide.

909
00:39:12,708 --> 00:39:13,958
怎么了 遗书写什么了
Why? What does the note say?

910
00:39:13,958 --> 00:39:15,848
你自己看吧
Read it for yourself.

911
00:39:18,688 --> 00:39:21,598
泰勒 你说的没错
"Tyler, you were right.

912
00:39:21,608 --> 00:39:23,558
我要为自己的行为付出代价 但是我不能承受
"I have to pay for what I did, but I can't face

913
00:39:23,558 --> 00:39:24,688
你给我选择的惩罚
the punishment you have chosen for me."

914
00:39:24,688 --> 00:39:27,528
你给他选择了什么惩罚
What punishment did you choose for him?

915
00:39:27,528 --> 00:39:28,808
坐牢
Prison.

916
00:39:28,808 --> 00:39:31,678
我告诉他如果我不自首 我就告发他
Told him if he didn't turn himself in, I would.

917
00:39:33,868 --> 00:39:36,738
安娜当年只比我女儿现在大几岁
"Anna was just a few years older than my own daughter is now.

918
00:39:36,738 --> 00:39:38,198
我夺走了她的生命
"I took her life...

919
00:39:38,208 --> 00:39:40,118
我选择结束自己的生命作为交换
I choose to take my own in return."

920
00:39:41,518 --> 00:39:43,488
安娜・珀塞尔
Anna Purcell.

921
00:39:43,488 --> 00:39:44,778
15年前死于一场
Young girl killed in a hit-and-run

922
00:39:44,778 --> 00:39:46,958
肇事逃逸
15 years ago.

923
00:39:47,908 --> 00:39:49,378
肇事的是你和盖文吗
This was you and Gavin?

924
00:39:50,668 --> 00:39:52,888
当时我们都磕嗨了
We were both high.

925
00:39:53,798 --> 00:39:57,218
盖文坚持要开车
Gavin insisted on driving.

926
00:40:00,138 --> 00:40:01,678
他撞的她
He hit her.

