He told me he'd rather die than go to prison.

931
00:40:14,018 --> 00:40:15,938
那你就什么措施都未采取
So instead, you did nothing.

932
00:40:15,938 --> 00:40:17,828
看看你的报应
And look how it turned out for you.

933
